# MCP Server Secrets
# ==================
# Store API keys, tokens, and connection strings here.
# This file is mounted as a Docker secret into the gateway container.
# Format for servers: <server-name>:<key>=<value>
#
# Examples:
# github-official:GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_token_here
# postgres:POSTGRES_CONNECTION_STRING=postgresql://user:pass@host:5432/db
# slack:SLACK_TOKEN=xoxb-your-token-here
